reviewText: Why on earth was Sleeping Murder re-written to such an extent???

In our world of entertainment, nothing is so precious than to have
the chance to seat down in a peaceful Home TV room at our Aussie
northern tropical atmosphere to watch "Agatha Christie's Miss
Marple Adaptations - Season 2" which itself is must for DVD collectors;
henceforth get your blu-ray copy from Amazon-com.
